---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import MobileNav from '../components/MobileNav.astro';
import PageHero from '../components/PageHero.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Newsletter from '../components/Newsletter.astro';
import MobileCallCTA from '../components/MobileCallCTA.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About Us | Holidays - Flights and Packages" description="Flights and Packages offer high-quality, tailor-made tours and holidays at the best possible price, with 55 destinations to choose from.">
  <Header />
  <MobileNav />
  <PageHero
    title="About Us"
    breadcrumbLabel="About Us"
    backgroundImage="/images/heroes/about-us.jpg"
  />

  <!-- USP Section -->
  <section class="usp-section">
    <div class="usp-inner">
      <div class="usps">
        <div class="usp">
          <div class="usp-title">
            <img src="/icons/location-icon.svg" alt="" class="usp-icon" />
            AFFORDABLE QUALITY
          </div>
          <p>Our travel experts spend time researching and negotiating to make sure you get excellent value but without any impact on quality.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="usp">
          <div class="usp-title">
            <img src="/icons/location-icon.svg" alt="" class="usp-icon" />
            CURATED TOURS
          </div>
          <p>Our tours are curated by our travel specialists and include plenty of personal touches, to ensure you have the best experience possible.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="usp">
          <div class="usp-title">
            <img src="/icons/location-icon.svg" alt="" class="usp-icon" />
            TRUST
          </div>
          <p>We pride ourselves on offering you the best service, with a friendly customer care team and a dedicated agent to assist you at any time.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="usp">
          <div class="usp-title">
            <img src="/icons/location-icon.svg" alt="" class="usp-icon" />
            HAPPY CUSTOMERS
          </div>
          <p>We are honoured to have received fantastic reviews from prior customers. Browse our testimonials below.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Intro Section -->
  <section class="intro-section section-container">
    <div class="intro-title">
      <span class="font-display text-secondary">Welcome</span> to Flights and Packages
    </div>
    <p class="intro-text">Proud to offer high-quality, tailor-made tours and holidays - at the best possible price.</p>
  </section>

  <!-- About Content Section -->
  <section class="about-section section-container">
    <img src="/images/about-us-middle.jpg" alt="About Flights and Packages" class="about-img" />

    <h4>Our Mission</h4>
    <p>Here at Flights and Packages we are dedicated to providing you tailor-made tours and holidays that are of exceptionally <strong>high quality</strong> yet still offer <strong>fantastic value</strong>. We're on-hand to help you find your perfect holiday, one that you will remember for years to come.</p>

    <h4>Personal Service</h4>
    <p>Our passionate and highly-skilled team build trusted relationships with customers, and work hard to maintain a connection with you long past the day you return from your trip. We are also focused on ensuring that when you choose Flights and Packages that you receive the highest standard of <strong>customer care</strong>. We know that it's the little things that make the difference and we believe your holiday should be nothing short of incredible.</p>

    <h4>Location Experts</h4>
    <p>As well as a caring customer services team, we also have <strong>location experts</strong> who curate our tours, creating extra special itineraries due to their inside knowledge. Our carefully crafted packages, which include transfers, excursions and many entrance fees in the price, have been designed to ensure you have an exceptional, carefree experience. We also offer you the chance to explore at your own pace and do your own thing, as we know many customers enjoy a balance of pre-arranged excursions and free time.</p>

    <h4>Handpicked Hotels</h4>
    <p>The wonderful hotels across all our getaways have been handpicked and checked on <strong>TripAdvisor</strong> for quality assurance, before being included in the itinerary. We believe that accommodation should be one of the many highlights of your trip, which is why we work hard to ensure our hotels exceed your expectations. We even have a collection of all-inclusive holidays, where the emphasis is firmly on relaxation and enjoying the resort facilities.</p>

    <h4>Our Background</h4>
    <p>At Flights and Packages we offer tours and holidays to <strong>55 destinations</strong>. Some of our most popular adventures include our <strong>Golden Triangle Tour</strong> in India and our <strong>Cambodia and Vietnam tour</strong>. We also offer a wide range of <strong>package holidays</strong> and <strong>city breaks</strong> with <strong>Italy</strong> our top-selling European destination. We hold <strong>ATOL and PTS</strong> so you can book your holiday safe in the knowledge you are financially protected.</p>

    <h4>Why Book with Us?</h4>
    <p>As well as our focus on <strong>quality, value</strong> and exceptional <strong>customer service</strong> our well-travelled, passionate team also have the <strong>travel expertise</strong> to ensure that when you book with us you can expect a wonderful time. Our location experts have multiple contracts with top international airlines including Virgin Atlantic, Emirates, Etihad and Qatar and through these contracts we are able to offer you competitive fares on flights from <strong>all UK airports</strong> as part of our tours and holidays. It's contracts like these that allow us to maintain our high quality but still offer you affordable packages.</p>
    <p>When you book with Flights and Packages, you can expect top quality at exceptional value. Start your journey with Flights and Packages today&hellip;</p>
  </section>

  <!-- Safety Section -->
  <section class="safety-section">
    <div class="section-container">
      <h4>in safe hands</h4>
      <h2>Total Peace of Mind</h2>
      <div class="card-wrap">
        <div class="card">
          <img src="/images/atol-logo.png" alt="ATOL Protection" />
          <p>ATOL stands for Air Travel Organiser's Licence and is backed by the UK Government and is the UK's financial protection scheme when you book a holiday with a UK ATOL holder. Our ATOL number is 11847.</p>
          <p>For more information about financial protection and the ATOL Certificate please visit the ATOL website <a href="https://www.caa.co.uk/atol-protection/" target="_blank" class="text-primary">Visit ATOL website</a></p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <img src="/images/pts-logo.png" alt="PTS Protection" />
          <ul class="safety-list">
            <li>PTS offers all member companies a trust account and insurance model which ensures all consumer money is fully protected.</li>
            <li>PTS members are fully package travel regulation compliant.</li>
            <li>All consumers can check the PTS membership of a company prior to booking. Simply contact PTS directly for peace of mind.</li>
            <li>If a consumer has any concerns about the allocation of their monies and the holiday supplied by a PTS member they can contact PTS directly.</li>
            <li>PTS is FCA registered to ensure trust and confidence when booking with any PTS member.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Newsletter />
  <Footer />
  <MobileCallCTA />
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* USP Section */
  .usp-section {
    background-color: #f5f5f5;
    max-width: 100%;
    padding-top: 40px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
  }
  @media (max-width: 450px) {
    .usp-section { padding-top: 25px; }
  }
  .usp-inner {
    margin-bottom: 45px;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 1240px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
    padding-left: 20px;
    padding-right: 20px;
  }
  @media (max-width: 940px) {
    .usp-inner {
      margin: 0 0 45px 0;
      padding-left: 20px;
      max-width: 100%;
    }
  }
  @media (max-width: 450px) {
    .usp-inner { margin: 0 0 25px 0; }
  }
  .usps {
    display: flex;
    overflow-x: auto;
    -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;
    scrollbar-width: none;
  }
  .usps::-webkit-scrollbar { display: none; }
  .usp {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-right: 25px;
    width: 290px;
    min-width: 290px;
  }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .usp { width: 260px; min-width: 260px; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 450px) {
    .usp { width: 223px; min-width: 223px; }
  }
  .usp:last-child { margin-right: 0; }
  .usp-title {
    font-family: "BentonSansMedium", sans-serif;
    font-size: 24px;
    padding-bottom: 20px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .usp-title { font-size: 20px; line-height: 22px; }
  }
  .usp-icon {
    margin-right: 15px;
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
  }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .usp-icon { width: 30px; height: 30px; }
  }
  .usp p {
    line-height: 24px;
    text-align: justify;
  }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .usp p { font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 450px) {
    .usp p { font-size: 12px; }
  }

  /* Intro Section */
  .intro-section {
    padding-top: 100px;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
  }
  @media (max-width: 940px) {
    .intro-section {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      padding-top: 50px;
      margin-bottom: 85px;
    }
  }
  @media (max-width: 760px) {
    .intro-section { align-items: flex-start; }
  }
  .intro-title {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: "BentonSansExtraLight", sans-serif;
    font-size: 60px;
    color: #000000;
    line-height: 60px;
  }
  @media (max-width: 940px) {
    .intro-title { font-size: 40px; padding-bottom: 20px; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 610px) {
    .intro-title { font-size: 36px; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 530px) {
    .intro-title { line-height: 35px; }
  }
  .intro-title .font-display {
    display: inline-block;
  }
  @media (min-width: 940px) and (max-width: 1260px) {
    .intro-title .font-display { display: block; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 530px) {
    .intro-title .font-display { display: block; }
  }
  .intro-text {
    display: inline-block;
    width: 396px;
    text-align: left;
  }
  @media (max-width: 940px) {
    .intro-text { width: 100%; text-align: justify; }
  }

  /* About Content Section */
  .about-section {
    padding-bottom: 80px;
  }
  .about-section h4 {
    margin-top: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    color: #424242;
    font-family: "BentonSansBold", sans-serif;
    font-size: 18px;
    text-transform: none;
    letter-spacing: 0;
  }
  .about-section p {
    line-height: 26px;
    margin: 0 0 10px;
  }
  .about-img {
    margin-bottom: 75px;
    height: 441px;
    width: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }
  @media (max-width: 1260px) {
    .about-img { max-width: 1040px; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 1100px) {
    .about-img { max-width: 880px; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 940px) {
    .about-img { max-width: 730px; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-img { max-width: none; width: 100%; height: 258px; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 940px) {
    .about-section p { text-align: justify; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-section *:not(img) {
      max-width: 730px;
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
    }
    .about-section p { margin: 0 auto; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 760px) {
    .about-section *:not(img) { max-width: 580px; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 610px) {
    .about-section *:not(img) { max-width: 500px; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 530px) {
    .about-section *:not(img) { max-width: 420px; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 450px) {
    .about-section *:not(img) { max-width: 365px; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 394px) {
    .about-section *:not(img) { max-width: 335px; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 350px) {
    .about-section *:not(img) { max-width: 290px; }
  }

  /* Safety Section */
  .safety-section {
    max-width: 100%;
    background-color: #F5F5F5;
    margin-bottom: 0;
    padding-top: 80px;
    padding-bottom: 80px;
  }
  .safety-section h2 {
    color: #1a1a1a;
  }
  .card-wrap {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    margin-top: 50px;
  }
  @media (max-width: 940px) {
    .card-wrap {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
    }
  }
  .card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: space-around;
    align-items: center;
    width: 610px;
    background-color: #ffffff;
    border-radius: 4px;
    box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
    padding: 32px;
  }
  @media (max-width: 1260px) {
    .card { width: 330px; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 1100px) {
    .card { width: 280px; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 940px) {
    .card { width: 450px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 530px) {
    .card { width: 420px; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 450px) {
    .card { width: 365px; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 394px) {
    .card { width: 335px; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 350px) {
    .card { width: 290px; }
  }
  .card img {
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    max-height: 80px;
    width: auto;
  }
  .card p {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 26px;
  }
  .safety-list {
    list-style: disc;
    padding-left: 20px;
  }
  .safety-list li {
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 26px;
    list-style-position: outside;
  }
</style>
